claims:
11. A method comprising:
generating, by a light source, a beam of light;
scanning, by a first mirror, the beam of light across a second mirror;
transmitting, via an objective, reflections of the beam of light generated by the second mirror to the first mirror;
capturing, by one or more devices, image data of a sample using the reflections of the beam of light; and
generating, by the one or more devices, an image of the sample based on the image data.
